Sentencas: Nanocrystalline strontium co-doped Samarium Doped Ceria samples with different compositions Ce0.8Sm0.2-xSrxO2-delta (x=0.05, 0.1, 0.15, 0.2) prepared by the citrate gel method.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction tools confirm the structure of the system.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: Field Emission Scanning Electron Microscopy images detail the microstructure of the sintered pellets grain and grain boundaries.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: The elemental content of the compositions confirmed by Energy Dispersive Spectroscopy analysis.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: The presence of concentrated O2- vacancies in the strontium co-doped Samarium Doped Ceria samples analyzed from the Raman Spectroscopy.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: Electrical properties of the sintered pellets are analyzed in terms of ac data from ac complex impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: Normalization of modulus spectra of the prepared samples shows the low value of stretching factor (beta) less than 1, which indicates a non-Debye relaxation process.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: The Arrhenius plots for all compositions show as the temperature increases; there is an increase in the value of conductivity, which indicates that the prepared samples follow a negative temperature coefficient of resistance.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: The combined analysis of impedance, modulus, and electrical conductivity attains value suitable for solid oxide fuel cell applications.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping

Sentencas: Among the different compositions, Ce0.8Sm0.05Sr0.15O2-delta samples exhibit a maximum conductivity of 3.39x10(-4) Scm(-1) at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Enhancement of electrical properties Ce0.8Sm0.2-xO2-δ by Sr2+ doping
